<unclear>sya</unclear> viśālakīrtteḥ</l>
<l n="b">
<unclear>pa</unclear>ṭṭa-trayārppaṇa-virā
<unclear>jita</unclear>cāru-mūrtteḥ</l>


<l n="c">śrī-śāntivarmma-nr̥pater vvara-śāsana-sthaḥ</l>
<l n="d">kubjas sva-kāvyam idam aśmatale lilekha||</l>
</lg>
<p>namo bhagavate sthāna-kundūra-vāsine mahādevāya
